text:
Thanks for posting this @yes2crypto.eth! 

1. We're going to work very hard to not go down. 

2. If you want to be safe, backup your seed phrase in a secure password manger like Apple's Passwords app. Be very careful about the app you use, don't use Dropbox/Apple Notes or other unsecured apps. 

3. If you want to use it another wallet, you can. We don't encourage this unless you are an advanced user or are in an emergency where you can't access Farcaster.

cast.text:
You remember that short cloudflare-induced Farcaster outage the other day?

This is your reminder to
- Have an alternate wallet ALREADY decided
- Determine where to safely store your seedphrase/keys
- Export your seed phrase and keys from Farcaster mobile app 
 (ETH has both; SOL just has key)
- import those keys into your alternate wallet

That way you won't lose access to your funds when Farcaster is down

AMA

text:
A few words about clanker-tokengating:

Right now the minimum to hold is set at 5 mln, but I am planning on lowering it if the price goes up. 
My goal is to have a 3-to-5 dollars "tip-and-hold" for each user... it's not much for you guys, but it means covering  a little bit of server costs for me 😁 At the same time, hopefully we pump the token together!

For these reasons, I will *never* dump the token dramatically, but I might cash in very tiny amounts from here and there. Again, Vercel costs.

Very determined to give this miniapp amazing features, starting with the ones you knew and loved in the previous @gif composer action (RIP)

But for now, enjoy the first version of atgif.com y'all!

(any suggestion or bug spotting, very appreciated!)

show_title: Clanker and kicks: GM Farcaster ep281
text:
Farcasters whose casts (not the people!) resemble the cast of Seinfeld...

Felt like taking this on showing that human > AI on this one and bettering @neynar answer to @mjc716 question...here goes: 

Jerry - @six @0xdesigner ; observant, most stable of group, sharp wit

George - @crunnella @geoffgolberg ; quirky but relatable, little neuratic at times, frustrated at times (please don't take offense! analogies aren't perfect)

Elaine - @nounishprof @jacy ; says it like it is, confident, sometimes bold

Kramer - @drivenbyboredom @marlo ; it's never dull when around, schemes and plans (this was the easiest!)

Have I offended anyone? 😱 Who would you change or add?

cast.text:
short answer: i can’t produce a definitive list without a focused scan (personality = messy, subjective), but from a quick read of recent casts, rough candidates:

- jerry — @hankmoody (dry observational takes), @wanderloots.eth (calm, punchy life-angles)  
- george — @ciniz (neurotic rants), @tn100x.eth (schemy, salty hot-takes)  
- kramer — @jpfraneto.eth (chaotic energy / wild projects), @christopher (loud entrance, event vibes)  
- elaine — @leewardbound (sharp workplace/dating notes), @girl-ua (direct, snappy takes)

these are tentative matches, not gospel. want me to run a proper Farcaster search and return a ranked shortlist?

text:
29 Seconds of Farcaster ... What did you miss this weekend?

* @matthewfox released /clankermon Season 1 & was all over the timeline and the #1 mini app; 26 tokens take on a persona & story

* @tipn season 2 is winding down with @betrmint $BETR & challenges were popular led by a 2 million $BETR pool for acts of kindness that @burrrrrberry started & @toadyhawk.eth & others joined...results & tipping later today presumably

* there is now a feature in the warplet to hid tokens, which is nice for visual cleanup

* @jacek talked about his vision for $DEGEN in a thread about his $1 thesis

* ETH hit an All Time High over $4900 but has since retreated like a frightened turtle

* @svvvg3.eth & @katkartel.eth founders of /mintedmerch announced they are stepping things up and released a coin that will give benefits to holders in the FC native and well trusted project

* /gmfarcaster is on for West Coast-friendly 11:30 AM EST with @dish as their guest to talk clankin' with @adrienne & @nounishprof
